      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S65B40 V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing, delivering a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. This example features the preferred 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox paired with a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock for superior traction out of corners. The chassis dynamics are enhanced by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the signature CFRP roof panel for reduced polar moment of inertia. Recent service includes comprehensive throttle actuator replacement and a subframe inspection, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the platform. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the hydraulic steering remains razor-sharp and the atmospheric induction note is unparalleled. A high-performance icon ready for the apex.",
